This README file contains information on the contents of the ../meta-pyro-updates layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Description
===========
This layer if for recipe and bbappends to get Yocto pyro release building clean on fresh
linux systems - specifically targeting ubuntu 18.10 or later.

For those companies using pyro for a product - this layer should enable you
to build the Yocto pyro release on updated ubuntu systems.

Security
========
While this layer permits the pyro build completion - keep in mind that pyro
is Yocto supported release any long - and thus security updates for pyro not done.

If your product uses Yocto pyro release - you should consider updating to a later
Yocto release to get security fixes as well as bug-fixes.

Licensing
=========
See COPYING file.

